  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nTurned out that autofocus is broken across the app. Originally found here https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/8687#issuecomment-519178199\r\n\r\n## Steps\r\n\r\n- open status -> tap access key -> keyboard is not active for entering recovery phrase\r\n- open status -> create new account -> back up recovery phrase -> confirm -> keyboard is not active for entering recovery phrase\r\n- open status -> profile -> advanced -> edit network\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nif `auto-focus` property is enabled, then keyboard should be shown\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/62850818-d1392e00-bcec-11e9-9640-6060761159d8.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
